cmake modules:
    * developed by humoto team:
        - humoto_add_regression_test.cmake
          adds a regression test for the core or a submodule

        - humoto_add_test.cmake
          adds a simple test for the core or a submodule

        - humoto_add_external_git_project
        - humoto_add_external_hg_project.cmake
        - humoto_add_external_svn_project
          wrappers for ExternalProject_Add(), allow compilation without
          Internet connection.

        - humoto_copy_dir_if_exists
        - humoto_copy_file_if_exists
          add custom targets to copy directories or files if they exists.

        - humoto_copy_extra_test_files
          add custom target to copy extra files for a particular test.

        - humoto_detect_func_macro
          check if the compiler supports __func__ and __FUNCTION__.

        - humoto_define_regression_test.cmake
        - humoto_define_test.cmake
          define tests or regression tests.

        - humoto_dump_variables.cmake
          dump all cmake variables (for debugging)

        - humoto_identify_git_commit.cmake
          identifies current git commit.

        - humoto_parse_test_dependencies.cmake
          parse test dependencies -- should be called from humoto_define_test
          or humoto_define_regression_test

        - humoto_list_filenames
          list filenames in the given directory

    * third party
        - FindEigen3.cmake
          find Eigen headers, copied from Eigen distribution

        - TargetArch.cmake
          detection of the target architecture, downloaded from
              https://github.com/axr/solar-cmake
